data.title: @m_koirala has separated from her Nepali businessman husband, Samrat Dahal. Speaking about her openness to new love, the actress expressed...
data.meta_description:
2,655 likes, 1 comments - bangalore_times on May 2, 2024: "@m_koirala has separated from her Nepali businessman husband, Samrat Dahal. Speaking about her openness to new love, the actress expressed her desire for a life partner. 

"I certainly feel the absence of a male figure in my life. If there is a partner, perhaps it would be nice to have one. However, I'll be honest: I won't wait around and waste my time. If it's meant to be, it will happen. If not, that's okay too. I believe I'm living a fulfilling life," she shared in a conversation with Zoom.

#manishakoirala #bollywood #fyp #bangaloretimes".
